-- variation: GumdropsElk9023

-- Describe a short walk used to estimate the solution to
-- a basic Laplace equation Δu = 0, using off-centered
-- rather than on-centered steps.

Domain U

Step x0, x1, x2, x3, x4

x1 := sampleBoundary( x0 )
x2 := sampleBoundary( x1 )
x3 := sampleBoundary( x2 )
x4 := sampleBoundary( x3 )

offCenter( x0 )
offCenter( x1 )
offCenter( x2 )
offCenter( x3 )
offCenter( x4 )

AutoLabel All
Label U "Ω"
Label x3 "…"
Label x4 "xk"


